ActTerritorial Lands Act
SubjectWithdrawal from Disposal of Certain Tracts of Territorial Lands in the Northwest Territories (South Slave and North Slave Regions) Order
PrecisWITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN TRACTS OF TERRITORIAL LANDS IN THE THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (SOUTH SLAVE AND NORTH SLAVE REGIONS) ORDER in order to (1) repeal the existing Withdrawal made by Order-in-Council P.C. 2012-410 of April 5, 2012; and (2) withdraw from disposal the surface and subsurface rights of certain lands (approximately 62,000 square kilometres) for a period of two years in order to facilitate the resolution of Aboriginal land and resources agreements.
